  "texts": [
    "Again, we follow the same convention asRinaldi & Del Pozzo (2022a), where 'astrophysical distribution' refers to the that from which the observed events are drawn before accounting for selection effects.",
    "We adhere to the LVK nomenclature, indicating simulated BBH signals added to the data as 'injections'.",
    "The code to evaluate our p det model and fit its parameters to injection results, and the resulting maximum likelihood parameter values, are publicly available at https://github.com/AnaLorenzoMedina/ cbc_pdet.",
    "This threshold between low-mass and high-mass regime is purely heuristic and not backed by any specific model or figure of merit.",
    "We defer a more detailed analysis of this threshold to a future work."
  ],
